nodes.name: inputPhoneContact
nodes.description: Phone contact. The client_id is just an arbitrary contact ID: it should be set, for example, to an incremental number when using contacts.importContacts, in order to retry importing only the contacts that weren't imported successfully.

nodes.name: contacts.importContacts
nodes.description: Imports contacts: saves a full list on the server, adds already registered contacts to the contact list, returns added contacts and their info.
